## 📌 Where to Put This File

Make sure `.gitignore` is in the **root** of your project:
```
rest-api-project/        ← .gitignore goes HERE
├── backend/
│   ├── app.py
│   ├── venv/            ← will be ignored ✅
│   └── items.db         ← will be ignored ✅
└── frontend/
    ├── node_modules/    ← will be ignored ✅
    └── src/